{"type": "article", "id": 23103, "title": "海洋生物灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-02T07:30:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702153240ldEghIRsfVKqOJzy.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组灯灵感源于海洋中的生物，比如硅藻、喙头舟形藻，使用 CNC 加工后的弯曲的竹材料，让它们有轻微的旋转感觉，很轻盈。光源在中间，能顺着镂空的结构投下漂亮的阴影。设计师长期生活在新西兰因而与海洋有密切的接触，<a href=\"http://www.davidtrubridge.com/\">这里是设计师主页</a>，他的很多灯都用纤细的竹结构做这种镂空的立体效果。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153236qkOln8z0LuHc9ebP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153237wOkY7FEIdNyisLB8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153238Jr73FIaYPxm0WNf8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153238UaILBXRZs9CWA2El.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153239owxOfn2S0ljLdm7B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}